				<td colspan="2"><span>Bards imho are the most difficult class to 2-box.  I recommend hotkeying the necro's stuff and spending most of your attention actually playing the bard.  With missed notes especially at level 58, you'll be hard pressed to have a twisting macro that works well, and you'll still have to press it every twist even if you don't miss a note.  (Insert Nostromo advice here.  I'm not going there.)
