				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: accnt splitting my 58 bard to duo with my 66 necro<a name="70242"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Nov 24 04 1:49 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Having duo'd with necros on several occasions, I can only say that they are one of the least likely duos I can imagine that anyone'd want to play.  Neither can take a punch (bards can at higher levels if you focus on it, but not at those levels), so the only real hunting methods open to you are kiting (fear, aggro, reverse aggro, etc.) And even then, it is difficult to keep aggro with your bard away from the necro or it's pet.  Difficult, but not impossible.  Either way, can you say boring...
<br />

<br />
Anyway, GL with that combo, if it floats your boat, enjoy.
<br />

<br />
Sinfonian</span></td>
